## Anti-Pattern'ler
| Anti-Pattern | Dogru Yaklasim |
|---|---|
| `useEffect` icinde fetch | TanStack Query |
| `any` type | Dogru TypeScript type |
| Prop drilling (4+) | Context / Zustand |
| Inline object JSX icinde | useMemo / disarida tanimla |
| State hem store hem URL | Tek kaynak: URL searchParams |
| Console.log production'da | Logger utility |
| Index as key | Unique ID |

